<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <title>Warner Bros Studios - Games & Apps</title>
  <style>
 
    body {font-family: sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;}

    h1, h2, h3 {margin: 1rem 0;}

    p {margin-bottom: 1rem;}

    a {text-decoration: none;
      color: #007bff;}

    a:hover {color: #0056b3;}

    .games {padding: 5rem 0;
      text-align: center;}

    .games p {font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.5;}

    .game-categories {margin: 3rem auto;
      max-width: 600px;}

    .game-categories ul {list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;}

    .game-categories li {display: inline-block;
      margin-right: 1rem;}

    .featured-games {margin-top: 5rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;}

    .game-card {width: 280px;
      margin: 1rem;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      border-radius: 5px;
      overflow: hidden;}

    .game-card img {width: 100%;
      height: 200px;
      object-fit: cover;}

    .game-card h3 {padding: 1rem 0;}

    .game-card p {padding: 0 1rem 1rem;}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <section class="games">
    <h1>Games & Apps</h1>
    <p>Explore a world of exciting games and apps from Warner Bros. Studios. Dive into thrilling adventures, unleash your creativity, and challenge your skills with our diverse collection for all ages and interests.</p>

    <div class="game-categories">
      <h2>Explore by Category</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="#">Action & Adventure</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">Role-Playing Games (RPG)</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">Puzzle & Strategy</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">Mobile Games</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">Educational Games</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="featured-games">
      <h2>Featured Games</h2>
      <div class="game-card">
        <img src="image1.jpg" alt="Game 1">
        <h3>Game Title 1</h3>
        <p>A brief description of the game and its key features.</p>
        <a href="#">Learn More</a>
      </div>
      <div class="game-card">
        <img src="image2.jpg" alt="Game 2">
        <h3>Game Title 2</h3>
        <p>A brief description of the game and its key features.</p>
        <a href="#">About us </a>
      </div>
      </div>
  </section>

</body>
</html>

